data.description: Located In the Desirable area of the Foothills! You'll Fall In Love with, This Partially Furnished 1 Bedroom, 1 Full Bath home. Newer 24'X40' RV Port, RV Access, RV Hookup, Storage Shed, Fenced & Gated. Must see to appreciate.
